<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<!--

Pedestal definitions to be used in HxLabwareEd2 during Nimbus multiflex carrier creation

displayName - name that will be displayed in pedestal selection dropdown lists along side model joiner; must be UNIQUE per each pedestal
displayPartNumber - (optional) string value, part number that will be displayed under displayName
pedestalType - string value (key), pedestal type that ties a group of pedestals together and is used to identify/use that group of pedestals in NimbusCarriers.xml when defining sitePedestalTypes
templateFilePath - relative path (within Vector's Labware folder) that points to pedestal template (*.tml)
modelFilePath - relative path (within Vector's Labware folder) that points to pedestal DirectX model (*.x)
imageFilePath - relative path (within Vector's Labware folder) that points to pedestal image (*.png)

-->

